description: Removes a previous export and the associated files stored in an S3 bucket.

parameters.name: exportId
parameters.description: The unique identifier of the export to delete.

nested_items.name: exportId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier of the deleted export.

nested_items.name: exportStatus
nested_items.description: The current status of the deletion. When the deletion is complete, the export will no longer be returned by the ListExports operation and calls to the DescribeExport operation with the export identifier will fail.
